sequenceDiagram
  participant U as ユーザー
  participant A as CLI Agent
  participant T as Tool Runtime
  participant S as Session Log
  participant L as Candidate Ledger
  participant G as Governance
  participant M as Governance Store

  U->>A: 失敗テストを修正する
  A->>T: package.json を読む
  T-->>S: observation: scripts.test
  A->>T: 运行相关测试
  T-->>S: observation: 失败日志
  A->>T: 修改代码并验证
  T-->>S: observation: 测试通过
  S->>L: memory candidate を抽出する
  L->>G: 出所/scope/TTL/conflict をチェックする
  G-->>L: 状态更新
  G->>M: 承認済み項目を長期記憶へ書き込む
